quran[339]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,Those ne expect meet us dir nur angxel ven us ni seg our Lord (ni tiam kred!) Ja ili committed gross arrogance produkt gross blasphemy
  25,22,Tag ili seg angxel ne est bon news kulp ili dir Nun ni irreversibly confined
  25,23,Ni rigard je all works ili done render them null kaj void
  25,24,dwellers Paradise est far put tag; ili auxd put news
  25,25,heaven romp apart mas de nub angxel descend multitudes
  25,26,All sovereignty ke tag aparten al plej Gracious. Por disbelievers gxi est difficult tag
  25,27,Tag ven when transgressor mord his man en anguish dir Alas Mi wish mi sekv path messenger
